---
// Local-first / ownership section.
---

<section class="local section hairline-top">
  <div class="container local__grid">
    <div data-reveal>
      <p class="tick-label">
        <span class="tick-accent">[07]</span> yours, on your disk
      </p>
      <h2 class="display local__title">
        Your notes are files.<br />Not rows in our database.
      </h2>
      <p class="local__body">
        Every note is a plain markdown file inside a folder we call a vault,
        on your machine, readable by any app, backed up however you like.
        There's no account to create, no server between you and your thoughts,
        and no exit interview if you ever leave.
      </p>
      <ul class="local__points">
        <li>Plain <strong>markdown</strong>, open it anywhere, forever</li>
        <li>Separate <strong>vaults</strong> for work, life, and projects</li>
        <li><strong>No account</strong>, no telemetry driven upsells</li>
        <li>Works entirely <strong>offline</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="local__tree window" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 120ms">
      <div class="window__bar">
        <div class="window__dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <div class="window__title">~/notes</div>
      </div>
      <pre class="local__pre" aria-label="Example vault folder structure">▾ personal vault/
  ▾ daily/
      2026-07-14.md
      2026-07-15.md
    ideas.md
    project log.md
    reading list.md
▸ work vault/
▸ research vault/</pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .local__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 6fr) minmax(0, 5fr);
    gap: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .local__title {
    margin-top: 1.1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3.6vw, 2.5rem);
  }

  .local__body {
    margin-top: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-2);
    max-width: 32em;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .local__points {
    margin: 1.4rem 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-2);
  }

  .local__points li::before {
    content: '·';
    color: var(--accent-text);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-right: 0.6em;
  }

  .local__points strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .local__pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-2);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .local__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
